description	"Archetype: Jedi Acrobat

Class: Jedi.
Class Summary: 
A fast moving dual lightsaber user with speedy attacks that excels at flanking and ambushes. 

Dual Lightsabers:
- Defense (2)
- Deflect (1)
- Can use Dual and Blue styles

Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (3)
- Pull (3)
- Sense (2)
- Speed (3)
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (2)

Attributes:
- No BP loss while jumping
- Immunity to Mind Trick and Sense

~Ahsoka Tano: Nicknamed Snips by her Master and known as Ashla after the Clone Wars, was a Jedi Padawan who, after the conflict, helped establish a network of various rebel cells against the Galactic Empire.
----------
~Aayla Secura: As a general in the Grand Army of the Republic, she commanded the clone troopers of the 327th Star Corps, with Commander CC-5052 'Bly' serving at Secura's side.
----------
~Serra Keto: A skilled user in Jar'Kai, Serra was known as Cin Drallig's finest pupil."
